  Thank you for your order #ORD-88421!
  Items: 2x Widget Pro @ $19.99 each, 1x Adapter Kit @ $8.50
  Total: $48.48
  Expected delivery: 2026-07-15
\`;

extractOrderEntities(email).then(console.log);
